content: I think I'll start with Lands End and the Sutro Baths. I've heard great things about the views of the Golden Gate Bridge from there. By the way, I was thinking of exploring the Fisherman's Wharf area again, since I stayed at the Hotel Zeppelin in that area during my solo trip to San Francisco from the 5th to 8th of December. Are there any good seafood restaurants or hidden gems in that area that I shouldn't miss?
